==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kalmia
<hw>Kal"mi*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. Named in
honor of <person>Peter <etsep>Kalm</etsep></person>, a Swedish
botanist.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of North American shrubs
with poisonous evergreen foliage and corymbs of showy flowers. Called
also <altname>mountain laurel</altname>, <altname>ivy bush</altname>,
<altname>lamb kill</altname>, <altname>calico bush</altname>,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kalmuck</ent>⟦br⟧
